reviewText: VERY INTERESTING BUT MORE OF A HOME MOVIE.  GLAD TO SEE THE INTEREST IN BULLFIGHTING AND THE ARTISTRY THIS AGES OLD SKILL PROVIDES.
Watch this video and learn a bit of  fascinating Americana. American bullfighters are real heroes of the rodeo. They put their lives on the line every time they're in the arena.

Anything that shows these boys jumping over those bulls has got my attention.  This tape is fast moving and lots of fun!  Ronny and Donny are my second cousins, and I know them to be nice boys too..but not tame..LOL!  (they come from a great family if I do say so myself!)
